interactions.flavorLineOne:
The AI of the Exodus Black was not designed to experience complex emotions. However, centuries of isolation and self-repair turned a relatively simple program into a complex neural web. In a way, Failsafe's grief, simply because it exists, is beautiful.

It just doesn't feel that way to Failsafe.

headerDisplayProperties.description: Cayde was the first sentient being Failsafe met since being marooned on Nessus. Check in on her to see how she's processing his death.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Failsafe

interactions.flavorLineOne: Leaving the cake on a nearby surface is the best you can do, but Failsafe seems appreciative of the gesture.
Failsafe hasn't yet tried on the earrings, but she's clearly quite impressed by the thoughtful gift.

"Accessing 'Friendly Greeting Protocol 6661E'â€¦ Corrupted.

"I apologize if I can't be more outwardly joyous without sounding sarcastic, but I am happy to see you. Probably."

interactions.flavorLineOne:
Failsafe commends you on the significant progress you've made on Nessus.

Continue your adventures on the planet to earn her gratitude and rewards.

headerDisplayProperties.description: Failsafe is impressed by your adventures on Nessus, and wishes to speak with you in the Exodus Black.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Failsafe

interactions.flavorLineOne:
Failsafe thanks you for the work you've done in securing Nessus.

New challenges appear on the horizon, however.

headerDisplayProperties.description: Failsafe wishes to thank you for your many successful adventures on Nessus. Speak with her in the Exodus Black.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Failsafe

interactions.flavorLineOne:
Failsafe congratulates you on your victory over Ghaul.

While the head of the Red Legion has been slain, the Red War continues across the solar system.

headerDisplayProperties.description: Failsafe has learned of your victory over Ghaul, and wishes to congratulate you. Speak with her in the Exodus Black.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Failsafe

interactions.flavorLineOne: You discovered the true fate of the captain of the Exodus Black. Failsafe thanks you so very much.

Failsafe, the Exodus Black's artificial intelligence, is ready to aid the fight against the Vex on Nessus. But now that Cayde-6 is out of his jam, it's time to seek out Ikora Rey. 

Help Ikora find what she's been searching for by completing mission SACRILEGE on the Jovian moon of Io.

Failsafe believes she heard the voice of her former captain over the comms network.  It's highly improbable he is alive, but she would be very thankful if you investigated the signal. 

Investigate the source of the former captain's voice, near the Exodus Black on Nessus.
Speak to Failsafe at the Exodus Black.

headerDisplayProperties.description: Speak to Failsafe at the Exodus Black.
headerDisplayProperties.name: Exodus Black

interactions.flavorLineOne:
"New Guardian Light profile detected. Welcome, stranger. I am your friend. Please remember this fact if and when I do not act like it."

Explore all that Nessus has to offer. Make friends with Failsafe, the manic AI. Discover the ruins of the crashed Exodus Black. And more!

Failsafe offers bounties, quests, and rewards to Guardians who complete activities on Nessus.

Find adventures, Lost Sectors, and public events in the world. Complete the tasks Failsafe offers to earn new rewards.
